description:
File &quot;ShapleyVIC_1.0.0.tar.gz&quot; is the archive file for the&nbsp;version of ShapleyVIC&nbsp;package&nbsp;used in the paper, which can be installed using RStudio menu: Tools -&gt; Install packages... -&gt; Install from Package Archive File (.tgz;&nbsp;.tar.gz). Refer to&nbsp; https://github.com/nliulab/ShapleyVIC &nbsp;for future updates.&nbsp; 

 Data used in Experiment 1 in the paper is provided as package data. File &quot;analyse_recidivism.R&quot; contains codes to reproduce Experiment 1 in the paper. 

 File &quot;analyse_mimic.R&quot; contains codes used for Experiment 2 in the paper.

